rows.name: Welcome to the Empire of Superbia.

rows.label: tlk45320152_01_msg0002
rows.name:
To reach the capital of Alba Margen,
just follow the path right there.

rows.label: tlk45320152_01_msg0003

The path terminates in the Cargo
Transportation Zone. From there, take
the elevator to reach the city proper.
